&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/21/12/alphabet.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 500px; height: 119px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The pattern followed is,&lt;/p&gt;

