&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Hence,&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;ldquo;KPT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;rdquo;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;is the odd one.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;सारणी&amp;nbsp;वर्णमाला क्रम संख्या दिखाती है&amp;nbsp;&amp;ndash;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/06/Common_Diagram_28.01.2020_D1hh2h1.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 500px; height: 119px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;अनुसरित पैटर्न इस प्रकार है:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/07/F2_Madhuri_State%20Govt._30.06.2022_D10.png&quot; style=&quot; width: 157px; height: 67px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

