&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/07/F2_Madhuri_State%20Govt._30.06.2022_D12.png&quot; style=&quot; width: 158px; height: 67px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/07/F2_Madhuri_State%20Govt._30.06.2022_D13.png&quot; style=&quot; width: 161px; height: 128px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;KPT&amp;rsquo;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;को छोड़कर सभी समान&amp;nbsp;पैटर्न&amp;nbsp;का पालन करते हैं।&lt;/p&gt;

